---
import GamesLayout from '../../layouts/GamesLayout.astro';
---

<GamesLayout title="The King's Search" description="The King's Search — an async co-op deckbuilder built for adults who can't find time to game together. Explore on your phone, fight bosses with friends. Free to play in your browser.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="game-hero">
    <div class="game-hero-visual game-hero-image kings-search-hero-bg">
      <div class="game-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="game-hero-content container fade-in">
        <span class="game-hero-label">Async Co-op Deckbuilder · Play on your own time</span>
        <h1 class="game-hero-title">The King's Search</h1>
        <p class="game-hero-tagline">Built for the friends you never have time to play with.</p>
        <a href="https://kings-search.quietatlas.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-large hero-cta">Play the Prototype</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="game-about container">
    <div class="content-width">
      <div class="game-lead fade-in">
        <p class="lead-text">
          Your friends are in different cities. Different time zones. You haven't played something
          together in months — maybe years. The King's Search is a co-op deckbuilder designed around
          that reality. Explore a few nodes on your phone while your kid naps. Your friend does the
          same on their lunch break halfway around the world. When you're both free at the same time,
          you fight a boss together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pull-quote fade-in">
        "Async when life demands it. Co-op when the stars align."
      </div>

      <div class="game-details fade-in">
        <h2>How It Plays</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Class-driven deckbuilding</strong> — Four classes, each with a distinct playstyle.
          Frontline damage, ranged pressure, party defense, enemy disruption. You build your deck
          across five procedurally generated stages — camps, towns, shrines, elite fights — and
          cross-player synergy cards reward the moments you coordinate.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>The extraction choice</strong> — In the second half of each stage, an abducted princess
          is hidden somewhere on the map. Whoever finds her becomes her carrier — she follows you into
          battle with her own HP. You can extract her early at camp or town for a safe win, or push
          deeper for better rewards and risk losing everything. Her condition shifts based on how
          quickly she's found and what happens along the way.
        </p>

        <h2>Co-op Without Calendars</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Async is the default</strong> — This isn't multiplayer with an async option bolted on.
          Async is how the game is meant to be played. Short sessions, every action moves the campaign
          forward. The princess's condition responds to in-game events, never real-world time.
          No one is punished for having a life outside the game.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Together when it counts</strong> — When players land on the same map node, they fight
          together. Combat is synchronous and turn-based, with energy and card mechanics that
          reward coordination. A duo can clear the game — but a full party makes it sing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="game-features stagger-children">
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Play Anywhere</h3>
          <p>Runs in your browser as a PWA. Phone, tablet, desktop — no download, no app store, no account required. Free to play.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>The Extraction Choice</h3>
          <p>Every stage ends with a decision. You've found the princess — do you take the safe win, or push deeper for greater rewards? The best runs are the ones where you almost didn't make it out.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Built for Real Life</h3>
          <p>Play a node during a coffee break. Pick it up again tomorrow. Your friends do the same, wherever they are. Progress is always forward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signature fade-in">
        <p><strong>Signature identity:</strong> A co-op deckbuilder for the people you never have time to play with.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info -->
  <section class="game-info container">
    <div class="info-grid fade-in">
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Status</h3>
        <p>Playable Prototype</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Genre</h3>
        <p>Async Co-op Extraction Deckbuilder</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Platform</h3>
        <p>Browser (PWA) · Phone, Tablet, Desktop</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Players</h3>
        <p>1–4 · Solo or Co-op</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta container">
    <div class="cta-inner fade-in">
      <hr class="ornamental" />
      <p class="cta-text">It's free, it runs in your browser, and your first session takes five minutes. Start a search.</p>
      <a href="https://kings-search.quietatlas.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-large">Play the Prototype</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</GamesLayout>

<style>
  .game-hero {
    margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--nav-height));
  }

  .game-hero-visual {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-hero-image {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .kings-search-hero-bg {
    background-image: url('/images/games/kings-search-concept.png');
    background-color: #0a0a12;
  }

  .game-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.3) 0%, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.9) 100%);
  }

  .game-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .game-hero-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .game-hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .game-about {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .game-details {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-details h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-details p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  }

  .signature p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .game-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .game-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .game-info {
    padding-block: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .info-block p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .cta {
    padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
